Reads the outputs of an M3 model fit into a list

Reads the outputs of an M3 model fit into a list

M3read(OMDir = "C:/M3", quiet = T)

Arguments

OMdir
a character string representing the location of an M3 folder containing M3.rep, M3.par and M3.cor files

Value

runs a list object of M3 outputs from folder OMdir

Examples

M3read("C:/ABT-MSE/M3")
